{"tid":2141700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許智峯談總辭「較多人盼寸土必爭」","createTime":"2020-08-06T01:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T10:25:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d052df61c7d780b5765c39625b3d1a2eb6c389f","tid":2141700,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T01:58:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/T5OK6N5WM7HCDHEQ5VARFOCBIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2FT5OK6N5WM7HCDHEQ5VARFOCBIM%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=82137478\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200806%2FT5OK6N5WM7HCDHEQ5VARFOCBIM%2F&h=3b95c56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200806/T5OK6N5WM7HCDHEQ5VARFOCBIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n許智峯談總辭「較多人盼寸土必爭」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府借疫押後立會選舉一年，現任民主派議員會否延任未有定案。民主黨議員許智峯接受港台訪問時，表示聽到總辭提議，但指有不少市民希望民主派寸土必爭，坦言民主派未有決定，惟一定會考慮主流民意作最後決定。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：以色列公司停售港破解軟件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n_Ok_w1B5ezNO_rGgheVsYwWBKQ=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BQDQU24IOKPZVCPVPV3FZGPPZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn_Ok_w1B5ezNO_rGgheVsYwWBKQ%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBQDQU24IOKPZVCPVPV3FZGPPZQ.jpg&h=a2f3c7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許智峯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考慮民意始作最後決定<br />\n<br />\n許智峯承認，聽到社會有聲音提議民主派總辭，「但我聽到較多巿民想民主派寸土必爭」。不過他同意若民主派議員被進一步DQ，連關鍵少數亦守不住，「咁入到去（立法會）個意義有幾大？」故認為民主派要考慮兩邊意見，以及議會過渡方案是否有合法性，「如果（政府）做法極度不合法，我哋係咪要加入去？」<br />\n<br />\n許稱民主派會考慮主流民意，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對被傳會遭DQ，許智峯批評DQ是政權極為卑劣的做法，剝奪港人參選權、被選權同投票權，「做法不公不義、令選舉公正受損，不論任何階段DQ任何人都不可接受」。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8e0d571315daa4d08d4b720c82a390e5c661ef8b","tid":2141700,"uid":